sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Attendee
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant Booking as Booking Service
    participant Payment as Payment Service
    participant MPesa as M-Pesa API
    participant Callback as Callback Endpoint
    participant Notify as Notification Service
    participant DB as Database
    A ->> GW: POST /api/bookings (BookTicketsRequest)
    GW ->> Booking: Forward Request
    Booking ->> Booking: Reserve tickets<br/>Check availability
    Booking ->> DB: Create Booking (Status: PENDING)
    Booking ->> Payment: Initiate Payment(totalAmount, customerInfo.phone)
    Payment ->> Payment: Generate STK Push Request<br/>(with timestamp & password)
    Payment ->> MPesa: Initiate STK Push (MpesaStkPushRequest)
    MPesa -->> A: 💬 STK Push Prompt on Phone
    MPesa -->> Payment: MpesaStkPushResponse<br/>(checkoutRequestId)
    Payment -->> Booking: Payment Initiated (checkoutRequestId)
    Booking -->> A: BookTicketsResponse<br/>"Enter your M-Pesa PIN"
    Note over A, MPesa: User enters PIN on their phone
    MPesa ->> Callback: POST Payment Result (MpesaCallback)
    Callback ->> Payment: Process Callback
    Payment ->> Payment: Parse callbackMetadata for mpesaReceiptNumber

    alt ResultCode == 0 (Success)
        Payment ->> DB: Update Booking: Status=COMPLETED,<br/>add mpesaReceiptNumber
        Payment ->> Booking: Confirm Payment Success
        Booking ->> DB: Generate Tickets & QR Codes
        Booking ->> Notify: Send Tickets & Receipt
        Notify ->> A: Send Email & SMS with tickets
    else ResultCode != 0 (Failed)
        Payment ->> DB: Update Booking: Status=FAILED
        Payment ->> Booking: Confirm Payment Failure
        Booking ->> DB: Release reserved tickets
        Notify ->> A: Send Failure SMS/Email
    end